{"tid":1760262,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國外交部召見美國駐華大使提出嚴正交涉和強烈抗議！","createTime":"2019-11-28T05:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T10:55:08.000Z","uid":41404,"like":150,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"a756fc1ab69aa423a6f9de77b29357ae5d0392de","tid":1760262,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"在北京，中國外交部副部長樂玉成召見美國駐華大使布蘭斯塔德，就美方的「香港人權與民主法案」簽署成為法律，提出嚴正交涉和強烈抗議。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成指出，美方此舉嚴重干預香港事務，嚴重干涉中國內政，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，是赤裸裸的霸權行徑，中國政府和人民對此強烈憤慨，堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成強調，中方強烈敦促美方糾正錯誤、改弦更張，不得將該法案付諸實施，立即停止插手香港事務、停止干涉中國內政，以免給中美關係和兩國重要領域合作造成更大損害。對美方的錯誤舉措，中方必將予以堅決反制，由此導致的一切後果由美方完全負責。"},{"pid":"4bdcd6acca7d9f49e5134e5008f7cc00aa110f00","tid":1760262,"uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e0f23ed49eaf1eeac3085d161ad2efefcae8ed","tid":1760262,"uid":122275,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T05:51:02.000Z","msg":"次次講都一樣 升下lv"},{"pid":"373d091f347edb09a818e3fd463932d1bd80c62b","tid":1760262,"uid":88167,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T05:51:48.000Z","msg":"今無人數緊出左幾多個部門口交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe96f23e5161d6bbb7ed673c422d3688c0821038","tid":1760262,"uid":23162,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢紙一張</span>"},{"pid":"370fce8c9046718961a7475c45404