本色；槍永對內，共狗專才！！<br />\n</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aa6774d1b9223c3dea4be92b4948937fa3f82dd0","tid":1760262,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"261a1e896f8b5bd0fea1f2bd2406f8435e4b7a0a","tid":1760262,"uid":291936,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:06:02.000Z","msg":"駐華大使: noted with thanks!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11af8712daf8bbb2aa7a788a97994d91b03d2d3","tid":1760262,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"廢紙你又理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e292b8d0049197fd9abee4478ebcb819053f388","tid":1760262,"uid":41771,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人留意到支共條底線不斷退緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人權法開始時就話聽證會係一派胡言，叫美國唔好信。<br />\n當有議員提出審議法案果時就叫唔畀交上國會。<br />\n交上國會後就叫國會停止立法程序。<br />\n立左法之後就叫侵哥唔好簽名。<br />\n簽左之後就叫唔畀實施。<br />\n<br />\n點解可以咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b145ceeb815f661677e1d17cb16676a1f566cedb","tid":1760262,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:20:17.000Z","msg":"支持支持<br />\n立即行政禁令禁止到美國留學/工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e5b9e8431e0deb8963b04fccb25451f8bcdb2a","tid":1760262,"uid":169665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"支共呢隻紙老虎一向只係識靠嚇<br />\n到最後又扮契弟和好一樣"},{"pid":"7efa973f5c7b88fbce275aae1010e79581439f04","tid":1760262,"uid":16534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:21:24.000Z","msg":"又話廢紙一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2213b9b48e5db50799c6f6ccbf1e821714714b98","tid":1760